{
  "stem": "23131.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he wanted to leave, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We sent him away, and from Vilna, we went to Bialystok to see if somebody is from my family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But when I looked at everything, I said, I don't want to sleep over one night here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We went through to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "From Warsaw, we went to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Lublin, we stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I think in Bialystok, somebody recognized him, too, Tovia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he said that he came for a mission from the place that he works.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They sent him for a-- for some business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in Lublin we were 10 days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And from Lublin, they got connections already with the Shlichim from Israel, and they knew already who Tovia is.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they told us how [INAUDIBLE], but we never went with the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We went with legal certificates with a Transylvania boat-- [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] a boat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was very little.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were the first ones to leave Lida.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just closed the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I left Persian covers-- Persian rugs that I picked up from the Poles in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I left everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just took a small bag in my hand, and I left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Closed the door, the radio was playing, and I left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't see him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] We wanted to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- I'm telling you, there were, in Lublin, when we came, it was already Shlichim waiting there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were already--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was the-- I was Turkish, and I was Spanish, and I was-- and Hebrew was my language.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all the idiots thought that that's all kind of languages I speak.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because that was the direction from-- from-- from Vilna already, how to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody gave us a direction how to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
